    >>> project.tracks["PIANO"]  # This is actually the same track
    Track("(MediaTrack*)0x00000000110A1AD0")

    But the same track can also directly be instantiated with:

    >>> reapy.Track(0, project)
    Track("(MediaTrack*)0x00000000110A1AD0")

